graph LR
    Feast[Feast Operator<br/>Feature Store]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    Feast -->|container platform| Kubernetes[Kubernetes 1.11.3+]
    Feast -->|runtime| Python311[Python 3.11]
    Feast -->|operator runtime| Go122[Go 1.22+]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional Storage)
    Feast -.->|optional registry/online| PostgreSQL[PostgreSQL 9.6+]
    Feast -.->|optional online store| Redis[Redis 5.0+]
    Feast -.->|optional registry/offline| S3[S3-Compatible Storage]
    Feast -->|default embedded| SQLite[SQLite 3.x]

    %% OpenShift/ODH Dependencies
    Feast -->|external access| OSRoutes[OpenShift Routes]
    Feast -->|cert provisioning| CertManager[cert-manager]
    Feast -->|metrics| Prometheus[Prometheus]
    Feast -.->|authentication| OAuth[OpenShift OAuth]

    %% Internal ODH Integration Points
    Feast -->|config injection| Notebooks[Kubeflow Notebooks]
    Feast -->|API calls| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API]

    %% Optional External Services
    Feast -.->|authentication| OIDC[OIDC Provider]
    Feast -.->|feature repo sync| Git[Git Repository]

    %% Integration Consumers
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|UI management| Feast
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|auto deploy| Feast
    ModelServing[Model Serving] -.->|feature retrieval| Feast
    TrainingWorkloads[Training Workloads] -.->|feature access| Feast

